        <ArticleTitle>The lysosome: a crucial hub for AMPK and mTORC1 signalling.</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>1453</StartPage>
          <EndPage>1466</EndPage>
          <MedlinePgn>1453-1466</MedlinePgn>
